[SN]TITLE[SN]
BBC Scotland's election coverage on Snapchat, Facebook and Twitter

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Wherever you are and whatever you're viewing you can keep up-to-date with the BBC's Holyrood election coverage.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Our political correspondent Nick Eardley has been taking your questions live on Facebook.
Watch out for more via the BBC Scotland News Facebook page.
We are also telling the election story through messaging app Snapchat - look for BBC Scot News. And join us on the website, Facebook, Twitter and Snapchat for a full results service.
As soon as polls close at 22:00 on 5 May, BBC Scotland news online will bring you the latest on desktop, tablet and phone.
